g.text: Etat de l’art des solutions d’orchestration des conteneurs
- docker swarm (multi-nodes, replicas, load balancing, rolling update)
global project: Cloud Native Computing Foundation (CNCF)
- layer service on top of layer container
- orchestration: gestion auto des conteneurs (deploy, update, supervision, ...)
* kubernetes (+ évoluée): prod, cloub hébergé (AWS, Google Cloud, Azure, ...)
- backup (snapshot ou plugin/exec db backup tool)
